---
import MainLayout from "../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
---

<MainLayout
  title="About Us | Bright Horizon"
  description="Bright Horizon combines technology, security, and African opportunity through practical execution and trusted partnerships."
>
<section class="soft-gradient border-b border-[#1F7A63]/10">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 py-20">
    <h1 class="animate-fade-up text-4xl font-bold text-[#145A46] md:text-5xl">About Bright Horizon</h1>
    <p class="animate-fade-up animate-delay-1 mt-4 max-w-3xl text-lg text-[#1A1A1A]/85">
      We combine technology excellence, security discipline, and opportunity facilitation for organizations operating in Africa's fastest-growing markets.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 py-16">
  <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-3">
    <article class="section-shell animate-fade-up p-8 md:col-span-2">
      <h2 class="mb-3 text-2xl font-semibold text-[#145A46]">Our Story</h2>
      <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-[#1A1A1A]/85">
        Bright Horizon is led by an experienced IT professional with over a decade of delivery across enterprise technology, information security, and cross-border business facilitation.
        The company was founded to solve two connected challenges: modernizing operations securely and helping clients access high-value opportunities.
      </p>
    </article>
    <article class="section-shell animate-fade-up animate-delay-1 p-8">
      <h2 class="mb-3 text-2xl font-semibold text-[#145A46]">Mission</h2>
      <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-[#1A1A1A]/85">
        Combining technology and opportunity to create practical, secure, and scalable outcomes through execution - not just advice.
      </p>
    </article>
    <article class="section-shell animate-fade-up animate-delay-2 p-8">
      <h2 class="mb-3 text-2xl font-semibold text-[#145A46]">Regional Focus</h2>
      <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-[#1A1A1A]/85">
        Operational focus in South Africa and the Democratic Republic of Congo, with a Pan-African network spanning key markets.
      </p>
    </article>
    <article class="section-shell animate-fade-up animate-delay-3 p-8 md:col-span-2">
      <h2 class="mb-3 text-2xl font-semibold text-[#145A46]">How We Work</h2>
      <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-[#1A1A1A]/85">
        We engage through a simple model: submit request, assess and structure, match and connect, execute and deliver, then support and scale.
        This keeps delivery practical for technology programs and opportunity transactions alike.
      </p>
    </article>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 pb-20">
  <div class="section-shell animate-fade-up p-10 text-center">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-[#145A46]">Work With a Trusted Partner</h2>
    <p class="mx-auto mt-3 max-w-2xl text-sm text-[#1A1A1A]/80">
      Discuss your next technology or opportunity initiative with our team.
    </p>
    <a
      href="https://portal.brighthorizon.co.za/contactus"
      target="_blank"
      rel="noreferrer"
      class="btn-primary mt-7 inline-flex rounded-full px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold"
    >
      Work With Us
    </a>
  </div>
</section>
</MainLayout>